Package: istatlab
Type: Package
Title: Download and Analyze Italian Labour Market Data from ISTAT
Version: 0.1.4
Date: 2025-12-11
Author: Giampaolo Montaletti [aut, cre] (0009-0002-5327-1122)
Maintainer: Giampaolo Montaletti <giampaolo.montaletti@gmail.com>
Authors@R: 
    person("Giampaolo", "Montaletti", 
           email = "giampaolo.montaletti@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-5327-1122"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for downloading, processing, analyzing, and 
    visualizing Italian labour market data from ISTAT (Istituto Nazionale di 
    Statistica) through their SDMX API. The package provides functions for data 
    retrieval, metadata handling, time series analysis, forecasting, and 
    publication-ready visualizations using ggplot2.
